Package com.iplanet.ums

Interface IAssignableMembership

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMembership
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssignableDynamicGroup, ManagedRole, StaticGroup
    public interface IAssignableMembership
extends IMembership
    Represents a container interface common to groups and roles. It extends IMembership by adding support for adding and removing members.
    See Also:
    IMembership
